WEBVTT

16:35.700 --> 16:37.150 line:80%
I feel bad.

16:37.800 --> 16:38.520 line:80%
It's fine.

16:38.690 --> 16:39.820 line:80%
Miss, your shoes and socks are soaked.

16:39.820 --> 16:40.630 line:80%
Dry them off.

16:41.280 --> 16:42.860 line:80%
I was getting stuffy in the carriage.

16:42.860 --> 16:44.120 line:80%
I came out for some air.
